[Guest]: I have understood that,

03:29:26.960 --> 03:29:27.960
[Guest]: okay, you are doing so much.

03:29:27.960 --> 03:29:28.960
[Guest]: You see so much.

03:29:28.960 --> 03:29:29.960
[Guest]: You understand.

03:29:29.960 --> 03:29:30.960
[Guest]: You think.

