[Amit Varma]: that I want to talk about.

03:29:46.960 --> 03:29:48.960
[Amit Varma]: And the first is this.

03:29:48.960 --> 03:29:50.960
[Amit Varma]: Like, I was with a friend in Bangalore recently

03:29:50.960 --> 03:29:52.960
[Amit Varma]: who works in a very senior position in a bank.

03:29:52.960 --> 03:29:54.960
[Amit Varma]: And he was complaining that,

03:29:54.960 --> 03:29:55.960
[Amit Varma]: boss, every time,

03:29:55.960 --> 03:29:56.960
[Amit Varma]: you know,

03:29:56.960 --> 03:29:57.960
[Amit Varma]: all the executives in my bank,

03:29:57.960 --> 03:29:59.960
[Amit Varma]: they go out for lunch or dinner or whatever.

03:29:59.960 --> 03:30:00.960
[Amit Varma]: It's so boring.

03:30:00.960 --> 03:30:02.960
[Amit Varma]: Because they don't have subjects to talk about.

03:30:02.960 --> 03:30:04.960
[Amit Varma]: I mean, they don't read books,

03:30:04.960 --> 03:30:05.960
[Amit Varma]: films, music.

03:30:05.960 --> 03:30:08.960
[Amit Varma]: It's entirely boring.

03:30:08.960 --> 03:30:09.960
[Amit Varma]: And this came to my mind

03:30:09.960 --> 03:30:10.960
[Amit Varma]: because earlier,

03:30:10.960 --> 03:30:11.960
[Amit Varma]: when you were talking about

03:30:11.960 --> 03:30:12.960
[Amit Varma]: your time doing CA,

03:30:12.960 --> 03:30:13.960
[Amit Varma]: or when you were talking about

03:30:13.960 --> 03:30:15.960
[Amit Varma]: your MBA this thing,

03:30:15.960 --> 03:30:16.960
[Amit Varma]: you know,

03:30:16.960 --> 03:30:17.960
[Amit Varma]: in some other interview,

03:30:17.960 --> 03:30:19.960
[Amit Varma]: that was how it was.

03:30:19.960 --> 03:30:21.960
[Amit Varma]: That their topics are limited.

03:30:21.960 --> 03:30:22.960
[Amit Varma]: You have other interests

03:30:22.960 --> 03:30:24.960
[Amit Varma]: in poetry and this and that.

